Sentencas: In a solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC), the high power output of interconnect/cathode interphase results from using a contact layer between both materials, which has adequate oxygen diffusion and high electron conduction.
Titulo: Femtosecond laser micromachining of metallic/ceramic composite material for solid oxide fuel cell devices

Sentencas: Ultrashort pulse laser drilling holes have been performed in a Fe-22Cr mesh dipped into LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-delta (LNC), LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-delta (LNF) and (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.95)Fe0.6Mn0.3Co0.1O3 (LSFMC) slurries to form alternative contact composites for SOFC.
Titulo: Femtosecond laser micromachining of metallic/ceramic composite material for solid oxide fuel cell devices

Sentencas: The optimal conditions to induce micro-pores with minimal damage in the suggested contact materials were 4000 laser pulses of 20 mu J and 40 fs width each one.
Titulo: Femtosecond laser micromachining of metallic/ceramic composite material for solid oxide fuel cell devices

Sentencas: The efficiency of laser micromachining in the studied specimens was independent of the ceramic composition.
Titulo: Femtosecond laser micromachining of metallic/ceramic composite material for solid oxide fuel cell devices

Sentencas: According to X-ray spectroscopy (EDX) chemical analysis, the laser effect on the initial elemental composition was very located without influencing the system performance.
